Package org.transitime.custom.missionBay

Custom classes specifically for Mission Bay Shuttle

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrDepGeneratorMissionBayImpl
    Handles generation of Arrivals and Departures by extending the class ArrivalDepartureGeneratorDefaultImpl but also logs arrival/departure information to the SFMTA API for tracking when tech shuttles are stopped at SFMTA stops.
    GtfsFromNextBus
    For generating some of the GTFS files for an agency by reading data from the NextBus API.
    GtfsFromNextBus.Dir
    A direction from the NextBus API
    MissionBayAvlModule  
    MissionBayConfig
    Contains GTFS config information of stop and paths for the directions.
    SfmtaApiCaller
